<div id="outline-container-org98ddde2" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org98ddde2">There are different types of hard work:</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org98ddde2">
<ol class="org-ol">
<li>Outthinking (a better strategy, a shortcut)</li>
<li>Pure Effort (working longer, intensity)</li>
<li>Opportunistic (positioning yourself to take advantage of change)</li>
<li>Consistency (doing average things for longer)</li>
<li>Focus (saying no to distractions)</li>
</ol>
<p>
Each of these requires a different type of hard work.</p>
